text: Vanessa Vélez (born 29 August 1989 Ciales, Puerto Rico) is a Puerto Rican female volleyball player. She is a member of the Puerto Rico women's national volleyball team. She was part of the Puerto Rican National Team at the 2014 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship in Italy, and 2014 Women's Pan- American Volleyball Cup. ==Clubs== * Gigantes de Carolina (2014–2015) ==Notes== == External links == *FIVB profile * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Puerto Rican women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Ciales, Puerto Rico
